These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, chinchilla, rat, rabbit
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the owner of the rat and the owner of the rabbit##7
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Pet   | rat | chinchilla | rabbit | mouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, nectarine, kale, pineapple
1. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
2. the person eating kale is somewhere between the person eating nectarine and the person eating radish##7
3. the person eating kale is between the person eating nectarine and the person eating pineapple##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food   | radish | pineapple | kale | nectarine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, peach, eggplant, grapes
1. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating grapes is somewhere between the person eating eggplant and the person eating peach##7
3. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |  2   |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | apple | peach | grapes | eggplant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, skateboard, boat, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere between the person driving the boat and the person driving the skateboard##7
2. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the boat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |   3   |    4    |
| Transport   | boat | trike | quad-bike | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, action, superhero, sports
1. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
2. the person watching action movies is between the person watching family movies and the person watching sports movies##2
3. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
4. the person watching family movies is somewhere between the person watching superhero movies and the person watching sports movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | family | action | sports |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, indonesian, german, argentine
1. the indian is somewhere between the argentine and the indonesian##7
2. the german is somewhere between the indian and the argentine##7
3. the german is on the left or right of the argentine##3
4. the german is somewhere to the right of the argentine##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |     3     |    4    |
| Nationality   | argentine | german | indian | indonesian |

