1. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person drinking water##7
2. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person drinking cola and the person drinking juice##7
3. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2     |   3   |      4      |
| Beverage   | water | cola | lemonade | juice |

